2. Create a template — Import an HTML email template or paste one in.
   VersionLab will parse it and identify the sections you can version.

3. Set up your audiences — Define the customer segments you want to target.
   The more detail you provide, the better the AI-generated versions will be.

4. Run your first merge — Select a template and audiences, then hit "Run."
   VersionLab's AI will generate tailored copy variants for each audience.

5. Review and export — Compare versions side-by-side, reject and regenerate
   any you don't like, then export the final HTML.

